                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="control-group">
                            <label class="control-label" for="Wx_UserPwd">
                                <span class="txt-impt">*</span>微信密码：
                            </label>
                            <div class="controls">
                                <input type="password" value="" name="Wx_UserPwd" id="Wx_UserPwd" class="form-control" style="width:260px;">
                                &nbsp;帐号及密码仅限智能绑定使用，不保存！不泄漏！不放心？点此
                                <a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com" target="_blank">手动绑定</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-actions">
                            <label class="control-label"></label>
                            <a class="btn btn-success" href="javascript:;" style="margin-left:30px;"
